parse(String) - Static method in class net.hypixel.skyblock.util.TimeConverter
Master Converter.
Converts a description of the ticks into the number of ticks.
parse12(String) - Static method in class net.hypixel.skyblock.util.TimeConverter
Converts a 12-hour description to the number of ticks.
The description is expected to String.matches(String) with "^[0-9]{1,2}([^0-9]?[0-9]{2})?(pm|am)$"
Uses TimeConverter.hoursMinutesToTicks(int, int) to convert.
parse24(String) - Static method in class net.hypixel.skyblock.util.TimeConverter
Converts a description of the ticks into the number of ticks.
The description is expected to String.matches(String) with "^[0-9]{2}[^0-9]?[0-9]{2}$".
Uses TimeConverter.hoursMinutesToTicks(int, int)
parseAlias(String) - Static method in class net.hypixel.skyblock.util.TimeConverter
Converts a description into in-game time.
Uses TimeConverter.nameToTicks.
parseTicks(String) - Static method in class net.hypixel.skyblock.util.TimeConverter
Converts a description of the ticks into the number of ticks.
The description is expected to String.matches(String) with "^[0-9]+ti?c?k?s?$"
Examples: 0t, 0ticks
